HTHT\" title=\"H World Group Limited\">HTHT</a></span>) in September, with my key thesis being that domestic travel in China remains robust and HTHT is in a great position to capture this demand. I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741841-h-world-group-demand-and-supply-environment-remains-very-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:36:50"}, {"id": "4741839", "title": "Cloudflare Shows That It Is '2021' All Over Again", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Social networking service. Streaming video. communication network. 3D illustration.\" data-id=\"1312417734\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3840px\" height=\"2160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">metamorworks</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Cloudflare (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NET\" title=\"Cloudflare, Inc.\">NET</a></span>) has been one of the stronger performers in an already-hot tech sector. The company is showing signs that an inflection in growth rates is coming ahead, which appears to have turbo-charged shares higher. But one could argue that valuations have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741839-cloudflare-shows-that-it-is-2021-all-over-again", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:34:37"}, {"id": "4741838", "title": "Trump And The Stock Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wall Street sign post with American national flags in background. New York city financial district, stock market trade and exchange, or business concept\" data-id=\"1143075035\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5649px\" height=\"3767px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sushiman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"Global investors are committing more capital to a single country than ever before in modern history,\" writes Ruchir Sharma in the <a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/49cca8d7-7b6e-47e3-a50c-9557d7c85fc0\" rel=\"nofollow\">Financial Times</a></p> <p>These investors are \"United by faith in the strength of U.S. financial markets and their capacity to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741838-trump-and-the-stock-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:26:03"}, {"id": "4741836", "title": "The Two Trillion Dollar Question And The S&P 500's Cautionary Risk Premium", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman Popping The Stock Market Bubble\" data-id=\"1264544465\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"4800px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DNY59</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The consequence of the re-election of President-elect Donald Trump is enormous. After the spike in inflation of over 20%, over the last four years, high hopes abound for the new administration\u2019s initiatives to reduce inflation. With radical reform promised with the so-called</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741836-the-two-trillion-dollar-question-and-the-s-and-p-500s-cautionary-risk-premium", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:21:58"}, {"id": "4741857", "title": "The Opportunities Across Private Equity's Current Liquidity Landscape", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A rising bar graph with a zigzag arrow\" data-id=\"1688772631\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By David Stonberg </em></p> <p>There are attractive opportunities for experienced liquidity providers in the current private equity market environment.</p> <p>Higher capital costs, dampened exit activity and protracted fundraising cycles have presented private equity (PE) sponsors with a fundamental dilemma: How to balance</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741857-opportunities-across-private-equitys-current-liquidity-landscape", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:19:00"}, {"id": "4741820", "title": "Copa Holdings: The Most Undervalued Airline Stock To Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"COPA Airlines Boeing 737 MAX 9\" data-id=\"1928902966\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Angel Di Bilio</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Airlines do not make for the most stable investments. The reward can be high, but that's mostly the take when you ride the waves rather than holding the stock through upward and downward movements of the stock price. Copa Holdings S.A. (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741820-copa-holdings-the-most-undervalued-airline-stock-to-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:10:43"}, {"id": "4741827", "title": "BrasilAgro Is Cheaper After Q1 2025, But Still Not An Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tranquil scene showing cotton growing in a field photographed from close up, Queensland, Australia\" data-id=\"1502913963\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Abstract Aerial Art/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>BrasilAgro (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LND\" title=\"BrasilAgro - Companhia Brasileira de Propriedades Agr\u00edcolas\">LND</a></span>) reported 1Q25 results, with an improvement in the margin of core crops (mainly soybeans from inventory carry and sugarcane from an improvement in prices). The company also completed the sale of one of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741827-brasilagro-is-cheaper-after-q1-but-still-not-an-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:03:15"}, {"id": "4741849", "title": "OPEC+ Meeting In Focus: Will Oil Production Cuts Continue Through March 2025?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden Oil Bubbles\" data-id=\"1170674069\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1150px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><e